## Quick Start

Install Node.js and then:

```sh
$ git clone git://github.com/faiverson/XMPP
$ cd ng-boilerplate
$ sudo npm -g install grunt-cli karma bower
$ npm install
$ bower install
$ grunt
$ grunt watch
```

Finally, open `file:///path/to/project-root/build/index.html` in your browser.

Happy hacking!